SPEAKER_00: A lot of those indexes and the funds tracking them look more like actively managed funds in the way that we've been talking about active funds, like concentrated high turnover, tax inefficient, higher fees.

738
00:58:30,080 --> 00:58:34,020
SPEAKER_00: They look more like that than they look like a total market, low cost index fund.

739
